接口 ValueFormatters.ToStringConverter

  • 所有超级接口:
    java.util.function.Function<java.lang.Object,java.lang.String>, java.util.function.Predicate<java.lang.Object>
    封闭类:
    ValueFormatters

    public static interface ValueFormatters.ToStringConverter
extends java.util.function.Predicate<java.lang.Object>, java.util.function.Function<java.lang.Object,java.lang.String>
    A generic Object to String conversion Function which is also a Predicate, and which only applies a custom conversion to targets that match said Predicate. Other targets are converted using String.valueOf(Object).

    • 方法概要

      • 从接口继承的方法 java.util.function.Predicate
